# 🚨 AI Early Warning System  
### Real-Time AI-Based Failure Prediction & Monitoring Dashboard

---

## 📌 Overview

The **AI Early Warning System** is an intelligent real-time monitoring dashboard built using **Streamlit and Machine Learning**.  

It continuously monitors system metrics and predicts potential failures before they occur using AI models.

This system helps detect:

- 🔥 High CPU usage  
- 💾 Memory overload  
- 💽 Disk pressure  
- 🌐 Network latency issues  
- ⚠️ System errors  

When risk is detected, the system automatically:

- 🚨 Displays a risk warning  
- 🔔 Plays an alert sound  
- 📧 Sends an email notification  
- 📊 Logs data into a database  

