## 🏗️ Project Structure

```
AI-EARLY-WARNING-DETECTION/
│
├── main.py              # Main Streamlit Dashboard
├── database.py          # SQLite Database Handling
├── email_alert.py       # Email Alert System
├── app.py               # ML Training + SHAP Explainability
├── anomaly_model.pkl    # Saved Isolation Forest Model
├── failure_model.pkl    # Saved Random Forest Model
├── shap_explainer.pkl   # SHAP Explainer
├── processed_data.csv   # Processed Dataset
├── monitoring.db        # SQLite Database File
├── alert.mp3            # Alert Sound
└── requirements.txt     # Project Dependencies
```

