---

## 🧠 Machine Learning Models Used

### 1️⃣ Isolation Forest
- Detects anomalies in system behavior.

### 2️⃣ Random Forest Classifier
- Predicts future system failure risk.

### 3️⃣ SHAP (Explainable AI)
- Explains feature importance behind predictions.

---

## 📊 Risk Classification Logic

| Condition | Risk Level |
|------------|------------|
| CPU > 90% OR Memory > 95% | 🔴 CRITICAL |
| CPU > 80% OR Memory > 85% | 🟠 HIGH |
| CPU > 65% | 🟡 MEDIUM |
| Otherwise | 🟢 LOW |

AI probability score can override threshold logic.

---

## 🚀 Installation Guide

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/AI-EARLY-WARNING-DETECTION.git
cd AI-EARLY-WARNING-DETECTION
```

---

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

### 3️⃣ Run the Application

```bash
streamlit run main.py
```

